dct_title_s: This Plan of the City of New York and its Environs
dct_description_sm: Sheet 1: Map was made for Sir Henry Moore and shows part of New York and New Jersey including: Paulus Hook, Hoboken, Bucking Island, Bedloe's or Kennedy Island, New York Bay, Red Hook, Hudson River, and East River with soundings.
Sheet 2: Map was made for Sir Henry Moore and shows part of NJ and NY including Paulus Hook, Hoboken, Bucking Island, Hudson River, Wall about Bay, Long Island, and the East River
